<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Complete Mechanism Catalog — Bot Rebuild Reference</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117; --surface: #161b22; --border: #30363d;
    --text: #e6edf3; --dim: #8b949e; --accent: #58a6ff;
    --green: #3fb950; --yellow: #d29922; --red: #f85149;
    --orange: #db6d28; --purple: #bc8cff; --cyan: #39d353;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); padding: 24px; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.8em; margin-bottom: 4px; color: var(--accent); }
  h2 { font-size: 1.35em; margin: 36px 0 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); }
  h3 { font-size: 1.1em; margin: 24px 0 12px; color: var(--purple); }
  .subtitle { color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 0.95em; }
  .summary-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin: 20px 0 28px; }
  .stat-card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; text-align: center; }
  .stat-card .num { font-size: 2em; font-weight: 700; }
  .stat-card .label { font-size: 0.8em; color: var(--dim); margin-top: 4px; }
  .num.green { color: var(--green); }
  .num.yellow { color: var(--yellow); }
  .num.red { color: var(--red); }
  .num.accent { color: var(--accent); }
  .num.purple { color: var(--purple); }
  .num.orange { color: var(--orange); }
  .num.cyan { color: var(--cyan); }

  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 16px 0 28px; font-size: 0.85em; }
  th, td { padding: 8px 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }
  th { background: #1c2129; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; position: sticky; top: 0; }
  tr:nth-child(even) { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
  tr:hover { background: rgba(88,166,255,0.06); }

  .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.78em; font-weight: 600; white-space: nowrap; }
  .badge-critical { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.15); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(248,81,73,0.3); }
  .badge-important { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.15); color: var(--yellow); border: 1px solid rgba(210,153,34,0.3); }
  .badge-valuable { background: rgba(88,166,255,0.15); color: var(--accent); border: 1px solid rgba(88,166,255,0.3); }
  .badge-nice { background: rgba(139,148,158,0.15); color: var(--dim); border: 1px solid rgba(139,148,158,0.3); }
  .badge-ironclad { background: rgba(219,109,40,0.15); color: var(--orange); border: 1px solid rgba(219,109,40,0.3); }
  .badge-spotbot { background: rgba(188,140,255,0.15); color: var(--purple); border: 1px solid rgba(188,140,255,0.3); }
  .badge-both { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.15); color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(63,185,80,0.3); }
  .badge-proven { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.15); color: var(--green); border: 1px solid rgba(63,185,80,0.3); }
  .badge-disproven { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.15); color: var(--red); border: 1px solid rgba(248,81,73,0.3); }
  .badge-invariant { background: rgba(139,148,158,0.15); color: var(--dim); border: 1px solid rgba(139,148,158,0.3); }

  .verdict { font-weight: 700; }
  .verdict-use { color: var(--green); }
  .verdict-test { color: var(--yellow); }
  .verdict-skip { color: var(--red); }
  .verdict-review { color: var(--dim); }

  .note { background: var(--surface); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding: 12px 16px; margin: 16px 0; border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; font-size: 0.9em; }
  .note-warn { border-left-color: var(--yellow); }
  .note-critical { border-left-color: var(--red); }
  .note-star { border-left-color: var(--yellow); background: rgba(210,153,34,0.08); }
  .note-green { border-left-color: var(--green); }

  .section-divider { border: none; border-top: 2px solid var(--border); margin: 40px 0; }
  .mono { font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace; font-size: 0.9em; }
  a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  details { margin: 8px 0; }
  details summary { cursor: pointer; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; padding: 4px 0; }
  details summary:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .errata { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(248,81,73,0.2); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px 16px; margin: 8px 0; }
  .errata-item { margin: 6px 0; padding-left: 16px; border-left: 2px solid var(--red); }
  .correct { color: var(--green); font-weight: 600; }
  .wrong { color: var(--red); text-decoration: line-through; }
  .toc { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 24px; margin: 20px 0; }
  .toc a { display: block; padding: 3px 0; }
  .toc .indent { padding-left: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color: var(--dim); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Complete Mechanism Catalog — Bot Rebuild Reference</h1>
<p class="subtitle">
  Verified scan: IRONCLAD (<span class="mono">spot_portfolio_bot.py</span>, 4416 lines, ~93 config params) +
  spotbot V10 (<span class="mono">btc-spot/spotbot/</span>, ~3500 lines across 20+ files) &middot;
  Feb 2026 &middot; Replaces previous audit.html
</p>

