<hr class="section-divider">
<h2 id="sec-K">K. Strategy: Exit Logic (6 mechanisms)</h2>
<p style="color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 12px;">5-layer exit stack, trailing stop tightening, emergency DD.</p>

<table>
<thead>
<tr><th>#</th><th>Cơ chế</th><th>Mô tả</th><th>Nguồn</th><th>Priority</th><th>Vị trí</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
  <td>K1</td>
  <td><strong>V10 Exit Stack (5-Layer Priority)</strong></td>
  <td>(1) Emergency DD → (2) Regime exit (optional) → (3a) Trailing stop after profit threshold → (3b) Fixed stop before trail activates → (4) Structural breakdown (optional) → (5) HMA cross (optional). First trigger wins.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-spotbot">V10</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-critical">CRITICAL</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">V10 strategy:341-400</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>K2</td>
  <td><strong>Trailing Stop with Tightening (V10)</strong></td>
  <td>Activate after peak_profit &gt;= 5%. Distance: trail_atr_mult (3.5×) ATR from peak. Tighten to 2.5× after 25% profit. Dynamic protection.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-spotbot">V10</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-critical">CRITICAL</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">V10 strategy:361-372</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>K3</td>
  <td><strong>Emergency DD Exit</strong></td>
  <td>V10: configurable reference (peak NAV, pre_cost, post_cost). IRONCLAD: fixed 20% gap from stop → soft rescue. Both: immediate market exit.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-both">CẢ HAI</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-critical">CRITICAL</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">V10 strategy:345-355; IRONCLAD:3945-3954</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>K4</td>
  <td><strong>Emergency DD Cooldown (Escalating)</strong></td>
  <td>V10: after ED exit → block re-entry. V1: flat 12 bars. V2: 3 bars isolated, 12 bars cascade (≥2 ED in 24-bar window). Prevent rapid re-entry into deteriorating market.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-spotbot">V10</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-important">IMPORTANT</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">V10 strategy:266-314</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>K5</td>
  <td><strong>Peak Tracking (Price, Profit, NAV)</strong></td>
  <td>Track peak_price (highest mid), peak_profit (highest % gain), position_nav_peak (highest NAV during position). Used by trail + ED. Reset on close.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-spotbot">V10</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-important">IMPORTANT</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">V10 strategy:316-322</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>K6</td>
  <td><strong>UDS Reconnect Freeze</strong></td>
  <td>After UDS reconnect: freeze entries for ≥1 full loop cycle to allow snapshot reconciliation. Prevent entering on stale state.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-ironclad">IRONCLAD</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-important">IMPORTANT</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">IRONCLAD:4155-4167</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

