<!-- L. CONFIG & VALIDATION -->
<!-- ============================================================ -->

<hr class="section-divider">
<h2 id="sec-L">L. Configuration & Validation (6 mechanisms)</h2>
<p style="color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 12px;">Config validation, safe-live defaults, live trading gate.</p>

<table>
<thead>
<tr><th>#</th><th>Cơ chế</th><th>Mô tả</th><th>Nguồn</th><th>Priority</th><th>Vị trí</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
  <td>L1</td>
  <td><strong>IRONCLAD Config (Frozen Dataclass, ~93 params)</strong></td>
  <td>All params in one frozen dataclass. Runtime, scheduling, assets, regime, indicators, entry, TP, stop, risk sizing, vol, breadth, circuit breakers, telegram, dry-run, orphan, safety.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-ironclad">IRONCLAD</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-critical">CRITICAL</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">IRONCLAD:1078-1244</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>L2</td>
  <td><strong>Config Validation (~30 checks)</strong></td>
  <td>Range checks, enum validation, timeframe parsing, logical consistency. Raise ValueError with ALL errors concatenated. Fail-fast on misconfiguration.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-both">CẢ HAI</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-critical">CRITICAL</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">IRONCLAD:1247-1359; V10 config.py:68-195</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>L3</td>
