  <td><span class="mono">V10 meta.py:27-33</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>O5</td>
  <td><strong>TTL-Based Session Auto-Expiry</strong></td>
  <td>Default TTLs: backtest 7d, research 14d, validate 30d, paper never. Opportunistic expiry on new session registration.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-spotbot">V10</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-valuable">VALUABLE</span></td>
  <td><span class="mono">V10 session.py:31-37, 196-219</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td>O6</td>
  <td><strong>Graceful Shutdown (Signal Handler)</strong></td>
  <td>Handle SIGTERM/SIGINT → set _stop flag → main loop exits cleanly → UDS thread stopped. Positions survive via persisted state + exchange stops.</td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-ironclad">IRONCLAD</span></td>
  <td><span class="badge badge-important">IMPORTANT</span></td>
