<!-- Q. REBUILD PRIORITY -->
<!-- ============================================================ -->

<hr class="section-divider">
<h2 id="rebuild">Q. Rebuild Priority Order</h2>

<div class="note note-green">
  <strong>Nguyên tắc rebuild:</strong> Infrastructure/safety trước, strategy logic sau. Không ship live trước khi có đủ safety layers.
  VTREND chỉ cần 3 params (slow_period, trail_mult, vdo_threshold). Tất cả complexity nằm ở execution + risk management.
</div>

<table>
<thead>
<tr><th>Phase</th><th>Mô tả</th><th>Mechanisms</th><th>Ước tính</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr style="background: rgba(248,81,73,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 0</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Type System + Data Model</strong><br>Bar, CostConfig, Signal, MarketState, EntryNavMode, Fill/Trade/EquitySnap</td>
  <td>A1-A7</td>
  <td>~1 day</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(248,81,73,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 1</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Execution Model + Backtest Engine</strong><br>Stateless cost, Portfolio, next-open fill, MTF alignment, warmup, DataFeed</td>
  <td>N1, N4, G11, I1, I2, I9</td>
  <td>~2 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(248,81,73,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 2</strong></td>
  <td><strong>VTREND Strategy (3 params)</strong><br>EMA trend, ATR trail, VDO filter. Entry gates, exit stack. H4 optimal. Indicators: EMA, ATR, VDO.</td>
  <td>J1-J3, K1-K3, J8</td>
  <td>~2 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(210,153,34,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 3</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Validation Pipeline</strong><br>Block bootstrap, permutation tests (EMA/VDO/ATR), paired comparison, multiple correction, timescale robustness. Methodology.md as spec.</td>
  <td>N6, N7, N8</td>
  <td>~3 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(210,153,34,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 4</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Risk Guards + State</strong><br>NaN fail-closed, kill switch, daily lock/limiter, exposure clamp, min notional, RiskState persistence, forced flatten bypass.</td>
  <td>F1-F12, H1-H5</td>
  <td>~2 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(210,153,34,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 5</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Exchange Client + Filters</strong><br>REST + signing, retry, time sync, Decimal arithmetic, LOT/MARKET_LOT, price rounding, notional validation.</td>
  <td>B1-B6, C1-C7</td>
  <td>~2 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(88,166,255,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 6</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Order Execution</strong><br>Deterministic clientOrderId, idempotent placement, status-unknown recovery, stop fallback chain, panic exit, min stop gap.</td>
  <td>D1-D10</td>
  <td>~3 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(88,166,255,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 7</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Order Lifecycle + Crash Recovery</strong><br>Write-ahead log, startup reconciliation, crash points, snapshot reconciliation, stop watchdog, orphan detection.</td>
  <td>E1-E7</td>
  <td>~3 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(88,166,255,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 8</strong></td>
  <td><strong>WebSocket + Live Data</strong><br>UDS, ExecReportTracker, event drain, rate limit, account cache, BarClock, parity checker.</td>
  <td>B7-B12, I3-I7, M3-M4</td>
  <td>~3 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(139,148,158,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 9</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Position Lifecycle (Full)</strong><br>Market entry, limit sniper, TP1, trailing stop, soft rescue, time exit, full close, orchestration, cooldowns.</td>
  <td>G1-G12</td>
  <td>~3 days</td>
</tr>
<tr style="background: rgba(139,148,158,0.06);">
  <td><strong>Phase 10</strong></td>
  <td><strong>Configuration + Safety</strong><br>Config validation, safe-live defaults, live gate, YAML loader, registry. Monitoring, session, metadata.</td>
  <td>L1-L6, M1-M7, O1-O6</td>
  <td>~2 days</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<div class="note note-warn">
  <strong>Tổng ước tính: ~26 ngày cho full rebuild.</strong>
  Phase 0-3 cho phép chạy backtest + validation pipeline hoàn chỉnh (~8 ngày).
  Phase 4-8 cho phép chạy paper trading an toàn (~13 ngày thêm).
  Phase 9-10 cho phép go live (~5 ngày thêm).
</div>

